{"tid":1808080,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"麗閣邨搜出 10 支懷疑曲尺左輪手槍　拘兩夫婦","createTime":"2020-01-02T06:54:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T06:56:16.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"31f5bcfa6536cc1c78a1a3bc3a18fa94f62e4b79","tid":1808080,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:54:29.000Z","msg":"警方表示，昨晚接報到深水涉公共屋邨麗閣邨麗芙樓一單位調查，發現單位內有 6 支懷疑曲尺手槍、4 支懷疑左輪手槍、86 發子彈及一副手扣。經初步調查，當場拘捕一對六十多歲夫婦，涉嫌無牌管有槍械或彈藥、藏有攻擊性武器及藏有仿製槍械被捕。人員檢走該批手槍及子彈作進一步檢驗，案件交由深水埗警區刑事調查隊第六隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E8%AD%A6-%E9%BA%97%E9%96%A3%E9%82%A8%E6%90%9C%E5%87%BA-10-%E6%94%AF%E6%87%B7%E7%96%91%E6%9B%B2%E5%B0%BA%E5%B7%A6%E8%BC%AA%E6%89%8B%E6%A7%8D-%E6%8B%98%E5%85%A9%E5%A4%AB%E5%A9%A6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E9%25BA%2597%25E9%2596%25A3%25E9%2582%25A8%25E6%2590%259C%25E5%2587%25BA-10-%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%2587%25B7%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%259B%25B2%25E5%25B0%25BA%25E5%25B7%25A6%25E8%25BC%25AA%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A7%258D-%25E6%258B%2598%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25A4%25AB%25E5%25A9%25A6%2F&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPkXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=c7010a03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E9%25BA%2597%25E9%2596%25A3%25E9%2582%25A8%25E6%2590%259C%25E5%2587%25BA-10-%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%2587%25B7%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%259B%25B2%25E5%25B0%25BA%25E5%25B7%25A6%25E8%25BC%25AA%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A7%258D-%25E6%258B%2598%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25A4%25AB%25E5%25A9%25A6%2F&h=c400d519\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E8%AD%A6-%E9%BA%97%E9%96%A3%E9%82%A8%E6%90%9C%E5%87%BA-10-%E6%94%AF%E6%87%B7%E7%96%91%E6%9B%B2%E5%B0%BA%E5%B7%A6%E8%BC%AA%E6%89%8B%E6%A7%8D-%E6%8B%98%E5%85%A9%E5%A4%AB%E5%A9%A6/</a>"},{"pid":"3e7498e8e53a66a0c74c1d05f1730f21b3dc0d16","tid":1808080,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r